data.description: Cute 2 bed 1 bath, 952 sq.ft. cottage with patio area.  Room for a bigger garage, chain link fence and cross fenced for your pets or garden, easy access to downtown.  Make your own workshop area, includes storage shed with plenty of room for RV/boat storage.
